cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with modeling and simulation of cellular networks. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the performance evaluation and optimization of cellular networks. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with the analysis and optimization of complex systems. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is a possible category as cellular networks can be seen as a collection of agents (base stations) interacting with each other. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with communication performance of cellular networks.
